                <p>An accordion is created with an element with a class <code>.accordion</code> and the accordion js module <code>data-js-module="accordion"</code></p>
                <p>An accordion item title has the class <code>.accordion__dt</code></p>
                <p>An accordion item content has the class <code>.accordion__dd</code> plus another element inside with the class <code>.accordion__dd-content</code> (due to the padding of the slide mechanism)</p>

